OL,7,FFormer Liverpool and Scotland defender
OL,8,FAlan Hansen has been discharged from
OL,9,Fthe hospital where he's been treated
OL,10,Fafter he became seriously ill.
OL,12,FThe club issued a statement on behalf
OL,13,Fof his family on Sunday saying Hansen
OL,14,Fwill now continue his recovery at home.
OL,16,FHansen had been in hospital since June
OL,17,F9 but the cause of his illness has not
OL,18,Fbeen publicly disclosed.
