OL,7,FIn a statement Liverpool FC said:
OL,8,F"Alan has been discharged from
OL,9,Fhospital today to continue his
OL,10,Frecovery at home.
OL,12,F"Alan, Janet, Adam, Lucy and family
OL,13,Fwould like to thank everybody for
OL,14,Ftheir wonderful messages of love and
OL,15,Fsupport.
OL,17,F"It has been overwhelming and has
OL,18,Fhelped enormously.
